Women are focused on relationships, so they like to scramble through such topics as who, where, with whom, how and why.
Probably each of us women has a bit of harmless gossip in store.
Hand on heart - that is probably characteristic of all women.
But this is not to be confused with gossip tanks of the coarsest calibre, to whom nothing and no one is sacred, who despise everyone in their surroundings and who represent a considerable danger, especially for women ’ s collectives.
