But Huntsman is not heard, because he stagnates in the depths of opinion polls.
Reagan's image
Romney had also vowed military strikes against Iran should sanctions to halt the nuclear program fail.
"If I am elected, I will stop Iran," he said.
"If Obama is re-elected, they will get the bomb".
He also promised Israel increased military assistance and accused Obama of failing to fulfill his obligations to this partner.
Entrepreneur Herman Cain, the second-highest candidate, displays a shameful ignorance of the file.
